00:03:51,732 --> 00:03:54,767
I wrote a paper
on our idea.

93
00:03:54,769 --> 00:03:57,836
When did my idea
become our idea?

94
00:03:57,838 --> 00:03:59,838
When I mixed it with
Sheldony goodness

95
00:03:59,840 --> 00:04:03,208
