Easy-Bake Oven of my mind.

96
00:04:05,245 --> 00:04:07,246
This is good.

97
00:04:07,248 --> 00:04:08,847
Our idea is really good.

98
00:04:08,849 --> 00:04:12,084
Well, the lightbulb in this
oven is ridiculously bright.

99
00:04:14,554 --> 00:04:16,522
You know, if no one's
thought of this, yet,

100
00:04:16,524 --> 00:04:17,823
