101
00:04:17,825 --> 00:04:19,291
Only way we'll
know for sure is

102
00:04:19,293 --> 00:04:21,660
if we post it online to
the pre-print server.

103
00:04:21,662 --> 00:04:25,230
I have it ready to go, but I
wasn't gonna do it without you.

104
00:04:27,067 --> 00:04:29,468
Wow, it's all
happening so fast.

105
00:04:30,303 --> 00:04:32,004
Should we just sleep on it?

106
00:04:32,006 --> 00:04:34,673
We could, but we
always run the risk

107
00:04:34,675 --> 00:04:36,675
of someone else beating
us to the punch.

108
00:04:37,811 --> 00:04:39,078
