are vegetarians,

205
00:08:36,183 --> 00:08:38,483
and I just bit the fingers
off your receptionist!

206
00:08:39,753 --> 00:08:42,988
Okay, we've seen plenty.
No!

207
00:08:42,990 --> 00:08:44,089
Give me the remote.

208
00:08:44,091 --> 00:08:46,658
Careful. She'll bite
your fingers off.

209
00:08:46,660 --> 00:08:48,760
Okay, well, I've been
poking around the internet,

210
00:08:48,762 --> 00:08:51,797
