223
00:09:24,765 --> 00:09:27,799
for Miss California Quiznos
1999, because I want to...

224
00:09:27,801 --> 00:09:30,002
Tell you what I want,
what I really really want

225
00:09:30,004 --> 00:09:31,870
I'll tell you what I want,
what I really really want

226
00:09:31,872 --> 00:09:34,039
I wanna, I wanna,
I wanna, I wanna

227
00:09:34,041 --> 00:09:39,211
Really, really, really be
Miss California Quiznos 1999!

228
00:09:43,116 --> 00:09:45,217
Play it again!
Play it again!

229
00:09:55,284 --> 00:09:57,920
Did he respond yet?

230
00:09:57,921 --> 00:09:59,079
Hmm. No, not yet.

231
00:09:59,080 --> 00:10:00,412
Well,

232
00:10:00,414 --> 00:10:02,081
maybe we shouldn't have sunk
to his level.

233
00:10:02,083 --> 00:10:03,782
It wasn't that bad.

234
00:10:03,784 --> 00:10:05,451
Read it back one more time.

235
00:10:06,787 --> 00:10:10,489
"My good sir, we are neither
crackpots nor wannabes.

236
00:10:10,491 --> 00:10:13,392
"In fact, we are
experts in our fields.

237
00:10:13,394 --> 00:10:15,694
"And while you hide
behind your anonymity,

238
00:10:15,696 --> 00:10:17,730
"we stand behind our paper.

239
00:10:17,732 --> 00:10:20,132
And later tonight, your mother".

240
00:10:23,503 --> 00:10:25,604
And you don't think
that's too rough?

241
00:10:25,606 --> 00:10:28,207
We're just standing behind her.

242
00:10:28,209 --> 00:10:31,276
It's not like we're gonna say
"boo" and scare her.

243
00:10:33,947 --> 00:10:36,715
How could you not tell us
you were in beauty pageants?

244
00:10:36,717 --> 00:10:38,517
