251
00:10:56,771 --> 00:10:59,004
Sorry, I had to get
the spotlight off me,

252
00:10:59,006 --> 00:11:01,774
and tearing down other women
is part of my pageant training.

253
00:11:01,776 --> 00:11:04,476
Okay. We are
reading that right now.

254
00:11:04,478 --> 00:11:05,544
