342
00:14:57,377 --> 00:14:59,478
And wishful thinking.

343
00:14:59,480 --> 00:15:00,979
"It stung Amelia

344
00:15:00,981 --> 00:15:02,748
"when he spoke to her this way.

345
00:15:02,750 --> 00:15:04,182
"In her little
one-room schoolhouse,

346
00:15:04,184 --> 00:15:05,951
"she was always
the smartest student,

347
00:15:05,953 --> 00:15:07,619
"regularly besting the boys
in her class,

348
00:15:07,621 --> 00:15:09,888
