349
00:15:09,890 --> 00:15:11,123
"this was a man.

350
00:15:11,125 --> 00:15:13,025
Here we go.

351
00:15:13,027 --> 00:15:14,526
"Cooper told Amelia

352
00:15:14,528 --> 00:15:16,194
