371
00:16:02,942 --> 00:16:06,311
You know what? A-At least
you guys did something.

372
00:16:06,313 --> 00:16:08,380
You know, you-you had a theory,

373
00:16:08,382 --> 00:16:09,748
you wrote a paper,

374
00:16:09,750 --> 00:16:11,650
